    ],
    "data": [
        [
            [
                "Dialogue"
            ],
            [
                "Huh, yeah... now that I see it, it kinda fits you."
            ],
            [
                "Hey... shifts ending in a couple of minutes. Would you like to wait for me and we get both ouf of here."
            ],
            [
                "Victor goes into the back of the store. I turn around and see the windows, it's all pitch black outside. When did it got that dark?"
            ],
            [
                "I see Victor outside the door and waves towards me inside inviting me to exit."
            ],
            [
                "I step outside into the street"
            ],
            [
                "It's getting a bit chilly today huh?"
            ],
            [
                "Hey did you heard that?"
            ],
            [
                "Hear what?"
            ],
            [
                "Rainfall pours abruptly just as we get far from the coffee shop."
            ],
            [
                "Victor and I rapidly begin sprinting towards the closest roof we could find."
            ],
            [
                "Oh, sh- hey are you wet? Im drenched"
            ],
            [
                "How bad gotta be our luck for this?"
            ],
            [
                "Right? And just as we were walking down the street. Hey... I think I see a bus station across the road, it got a roof."
            ],
            [
                "Would you..."
            ],
            [
                "Let you be my company on my way home?"
            ],
            [
                "Yeah... right out of my mouth."
            ],
            [
                "Mmm, yeah?"
            ],
            [
                "Really?"
            ],
            [
                "What else I'm gonna do? I'll get on the bus eitherway I'm soaked wet."
            ],
            [
                "We run across the street reaching for the bus station, Victor tries to use [his] backpack as cover, with very little effect."
            ],
            [
                "The bus arrives and we board it. The bus is a little bit full and there is not much space but a pair of seats."
            ],
            [
                "Victor gets the window side."
            ],
            [
                "There is something captivating in [his] stare towards the world."
            ],
            [
                "Is something relaxing."
            ],
            [
                "Is ver..."
            ],
            [
                "....."
            ],
            [
                "........"
            ],
            [
                "................"
            ],
            [
                "......................."
            ],
            [
                "Hey! hey [tn] are you, alright?"
            ],
            [
                "I bump my head up as I realise I was sleeping."
            ],
            [
                "I see a stain in Victor's shirt."
            ],
            [
                "So, sorry.... Dang.. sorry Victor."
            ],
            [
                "Huh? this? it's okay. I was gonna end up washing my clothes either way."
            ],
            [
                "STOPPING AT HAZEL STREET"
            ],
            [
                "OH, damn it's my stop. I gotta get out."
            ],
            [
                "I get up quickly and try to gather myself to step out of the bus."
            ],
            [
                "Victor also gets up and follows me up until the bus doors."
            ],
            [
                "Hey, it's my stop, so... goodbye, it was nice Victor!"
            ],
            [
                "Hey [tn]!"
            ],
            [
                "Victor leans over the open doors trying to push [him]self out of the bus without stepping out."
            ],
            [
                "[tn], will I see you again? Tomorrow? Or, some other day?"
            ],
            [
                ".... We could, hang out some other time?"
            ],
            [
                "Yeah, Sure, I could pass by. Get another cup of coffee."
            ],
            [
                "No, not that, Sh.. I'm not good with words."
            ],
            [
                "What I'm trying to say is that I-"
            ],
            [
                "HEY GET OUT OF THERE ALREADY"
            ],
            [
                "HEY I'M TALKING TO HER, SHUT UP"
            ],
            [
                "YOU SHUT UP ALREADY, OR I'LL STEP IT ALL DOWN UNTIL YOU FALL DOWN TO THE ASPHALT."
            ],
            [
                "[tn]! What I wanted to say is that...I..."
            ],
            [
                "Is that I really enjoy... talking to you."
            ],
            [
                "Uh, yeah! me too!"
            ],
            [
                "No, I wanted to tell you, that I."
            ],
            [
                "I.... I"
            ],
            [
                "I really lo-"
            ],
            [
                "THAT'S IT IM NOT PAID ENOUGHT TO GET HOME LATE!"
            ],
            [
                "The bus driver furiously rushes the bus and closes the doors while Victor shakes barely falling out of the bus."
            ],
            [
                "The bus leaves among the rain."
            ],
            [
                "...."
            ],
            [
                "Huh...."
            ],
            [
                "I make my way home, and just as I enter I find helpie in the kitchen preparing what seems to be food."
            ],
            [
                "Hey! [tn]! What time is it already?"
            ],
            [
                "What? What's the issue?"
            ],
            [
                "You ran out and never came home until this late."
            ],
            [
                "What even happened?"
            ],
            [
                "After all the running, I'm feeling to exhausted to even talk anything out."
            ],
            [
                "I'm just gonna sleep."
            ],
            [
                "Not even going to dinner? What's wrong with you?"
            ],
            [
                "I head to my room and close the door."
            ],
            [
                "What a trip"
            ],
            [
                "I go to sleep........."
            ],
            [
                "The birds chirp and the warm light of sun wakes me up."
            ],
